where I feel regret and guilt

00:25:00.066 --> 00:25:03.035 align:middle line:84%
and depress and sad
and a victim.

00:25:03.035 --> 00:25:04.036 align:middle line:90%
>> LG: Ah-huh.

00:25:04.036 --> 00:25:05.237 align:middle line:84%
>> RM: And same thing
with the future.

00:25:05.237 --> 00:25:07.340 align:middle line:84%
You're going either
anticipate the future

00:25:07.340 --> 00:25:10.509 align:middle line:84%
with positive expectancy,
eagerness, and hope,

00:25:10.509 --> 00:25:13.079 align:middle line:84%
and excitement, or
negative expectancy.

00:25:13.079 --> 00:25:15.615 align:middle line:84%
>> LG: So each one of
those a littler mini nows,

00:25:15.615 --> 00:25:16.849 align:middle line:90%
is that what you say?

00:25:16.849 --> 00:25:20.019 align:middle line:84%
>> RM: Almost-- The only
now most people know except

