but the surfer that goes back
to surf everyday wants to be

00:25:27.627 --> 00:25:29.662 align:middle line:90%
in the center of that mandala.

00:25:29.662 --> 00:25:30.162 align:middle line:90%
>> LG: Ah-huh.

00:25:30.162 --> 00:25:31.130 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: OK.

00:25:31.130 --> 00:25:31.664 align:middle line:84%
The dancer, who wants
to let go--

00:25:31.664 --> 00:25:32.431 align:middle line:90%
>> LG: Yes.

00:25:32.431 --> 00:25:32.965 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: -- and be danced--

00:25:32.965 --> 00:25:34.066 align:middle line:90%
>> LG: Yes.

00:25:34.066 --> 00:25:35.468 align:middle line:84%
>> RM: -- you know,
[inaudible] song maniac.

