of the time almost everybody
is living in the now created

00:25:44.410 --> 00:25:47.046 align:middle line:84%
by their future thoughts, their
past thoughts, their judgment

00:25:47.046 --> 00:25:48.748 align:middle line:84%
of themselves, the
judgment of others,

00:25:48.748 --> 00:25:50.883 align:middle line:90%
and you can learn to watch that.

